{"tid":1721283,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人知戰場上最缺乏係咩？？？","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:15:22.000Z","uid":245371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d77e103ec241de56f09593c152f9693be79471e9","tid":1721283,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"最缺係哨兵呀！！！<br />\n哨兵！！哨兵！！！哨兵！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n要有人keep住比有用資訊手足做野先做得放心，逃走路線都容易計劃！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">哨兵同傳訊師</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n落去既的確有唔少小隊，但亦都好多好多單拖！！！<br />\n唔該小隊有哨兵既同晒全部手足報一報最緊急同有用既資訊，做多呢一步就救到好多手足架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算比內鬼知道又如何，手足唔知就少左份防範同危急應變反應慢左，而且大機會唔好彩就中伏，唔該做多一步！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以唔講自己移動位置同目標（怕比內鬼知道設局），但你要講邊度有危險等所有人有防範同心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"c0d809cb65bdd164473f2fcc1f51a1de68cf364d","tid":1721283,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9961209a9e16c4790b88fb2a88d2664d0d87fde","tid":1721283,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"係軍妓"},{"pid":"5047e463fe9c5259e7a31d6c837323cf5d31a435","tid":1721283,"uid":314909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9961209a9e16c4790b88fb2a88d2664d0d87fde","tid":1721283,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"係軍妓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你，你老母就軍妓"},{"pid":"b36a7a05183b85aa97513ccfeb8b70611d